  // Discernment Clouded: An event that impairs judgment
  "id": "discernment_clouded",
  "title": "When Clarity Becomes Confusion",
  "description": "Something undermines your ability to judge accurately, leaving you uncertain of what's real.",
  "content": "You thought you understood the situation, but new information contradicts what seemed obvious. Or maybe you trusted your judgment about someone, only to be proven spectacularly wrong. Or perhaps you're just exhausted, overwhelmed, emotionally compromised—and you realize your usually reliable instincts are failing you. The confidence you had in your ability to read people and situations has been shaken. You're second-guessing everything.",
