    {
      "id": "analyze_failure",
      "text": "Figure out specifically where your judgment failed",
      "description": "This is data about how you can improve.",
      "resultText": "You resist the urge to panic and instead methodically examine where your discernment broke down. What assumptions did you make? What evidence did you ignore? What emotional factors clouded your judgment? The analysis is humbling but illuminating. You identify specific weaknesses in your thinking—biases you didn't know you had, shortcuts you unconsciously took. Your judgment is temporarily impaired, but you're gaining insight into how to improve it.",
